==Russian==

===Pronunciation===
This letter has no pronunciation of its own. It instead functions as a graphic sign.

===Letter===
{{head|ru|letter|lower case||upper case|Ъ|tr=-}}

# The letter {{m|ru|твёрдый знак||hard sign}}, the twenty-eighth letter of the [[Russian]] alphabet

====Usage notes====
In Russian, this letter has no sound of its own, but modifies that of the preceding consonant, causing it to be pronounced hard (i.e., unpalatalized). Some writers use <big>'</big> (apostrophe) instead of {{m|ru||ъ|tr=-}}, e.g. {{m|ru|съезд}} — {{m|ru||с'езд}}, which is considered non-standard or obsolete. After the 1918 spelling reform when the usage of {{m|ru||ъ|tr=-}} was heavily reduced, some typewriters did not have the letter at all, forcing people to use <big>'</big> (apostrophe).

